# Lab state policy:
# - Track small durable research/control-plane files under .omx/research/ and
#   selected .omx/state/*.md files.
# - Do not track raw provider state, local logs, caches, or rebuildable/hosted
#   artifacts. Canonicalize them into .omx/research ledgers or externalize them
#   with a committed manifest.
# Audit the boundary with:
#   python tools/audit_research_state_tracking.py --repo-root .
#
# Queue-owned storage preflight plans can contain machine-local volume choices,
# cleanup candidates, and cold-store paths. Preserve their durable findings in
# dated Codex/Claude memos; keep the per-run JSON plan/journal files local.
.omx/research/dqs1_local_first_storage_plan_*.json
.omx/research/dqs1_local_first_proactive_cleanup_*.json
.omx/research/dqs1_local_first_proactive_cleanup_*.json.journal.jsonl
.omx/research/byte_shaving_materializer_storage_plan_*.json
.omx/research/byte_shaving_materializer_proactive_cleanup_*.json
.omx/research/byte_shaving_materializer_proactive_cleanup_*.json.journal.jsonl
.omx/research/*_storage_plan_*.json
.omx/research/*_proactive_cleanup_*.json
.omx/research/*_proactive_cleanup_*.json.journal.jsonl
.omx/research/*_artifact_retention_*.json
.omx/research/*_artifact_retention_*.json.journal.jsonl
.omx/research/local_training_execution_queue*.json
.omx/research/local_training_execution_plan*.json
.omx/research/inverse_steganalysis_action_functional*.json
.omx/research/inverse_steganalysis_action_functional*.md
# Generated materializer harvest/exact-readiness/dispatch handoff JSON is
